name: {DD} Biting lips SFW semirealistic/realistic version
description:
This Lora represents a concept of lip biting. I've never been able to make it with any model I have before. This Lora gives a pretty decent results, but it's not very stable and not very flexible. I get about 2-3 images that I like per generation.

Tags

DDbitlip

Additional tags

*You may use it if nothing else works

Close-up portrait

Negative tags

Any of the following bw/monochrome/grayscale

Enjoy)

Feel free to ask any questions here in comments, or in my discord channel.

Also I am making games with AI arts. They will be free in the future, but if you want to participate in making or have an early access - you can support me on patreon)
